{"tid":2407162,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"剛才惡補了相對論","createTime":"2021-02-13T19:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T11:15:56.000Z","uid":47901,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"da7f5eb4c66f1540e8b43100c45d36b24ae64b7c","tid":2407162,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T19:50:36.000Z","msg":"請評一評！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">牛頓：KE=mv^2</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">愛恩斯坦：E=mc^2</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當人坐係度,或者行緊,或者跑緊（在任何地方）觀察一件object<br />\n<br />\nobject速度增加，<br />\nKE就會增加，<br />\nE就會相等地增加（因為E包含了KE在其中）<br />\n<br />\n當object速度不斷增加，KE就趨向<span class=\"pink\">無限</span>，E就趨向 E+<span class=\"pink\">無限</span>（因為E包含了KE在其中）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從上文愛恩斯坦的公式，<br />\n可知 <span class=\"gold\">m=E/(c^2)</span>，<br />\n因此，m就趨向 <span class=\"limegreen\">(E+無限)/(c^2)</span>, <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從上文牛頓的公式，<br />\n可知 <span class=\"teal\">v^2=KE/m</span><br />\n因此, v^2就趨向 <span class=\"pink\">無限</span>/<span class=\"limegreen\">(E+無限)*(c^2)</span>,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於E愈來愈微不足道，<br />\n所以，v就越向c,<br />\n<br />\n所以當object的速度不斷增加，速度趨向光速"},{"pid":"5763344b4fe592901fc6df1b4ab389c31d0f405d","tid":2407162,"uid":371721,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T19:55:33.000Z","msg":"E^2 = p^2 c^2 + m^2 c^4<br />\n<br />\n此post已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b607c83dfa435275f8dca9fc85c13b43d1581e3","tid":2407162,"uid":226739,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T19:59:39.000Z","msg":"牛頓果個係力學<br />\n<br />\nEinstein 果個係質能互換<br />\n<br />\n好似係兩樣嘢黎wor, 點可以話E 包含喺KE 入面呀？<br />\n<br />\n利申 phy攞5"},{"pid":"3b8550fa512411ccf89ee8f3d6c7efeba5a391d4","tid":2407162,"uid":25260,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T20:02:13.000Z","msg":"根據我中學僅餘嘅物理知識，<br />\n<br />\n唔係 KE = (mv^2)/2 咩？"},{"pid":